hopobject.body: I can't get through at the moment twittervenezuela.co “There are thousands of Conservatives who agree with what we’re doing. Well I’m sorry Mr Hammond finds that embarrassing. Not half as embarrassing as it is for me looking in the faces of some of our young soldiers who have come back from Afghanistan and been told they are redundant or they’re going to be posted to regiments they’ve never heard of to support them. This isn’t the way we treat our Forces.”
